  "notes": [
    {
      "id": "note-rest-rules",
      "title": "Resting at Camp (SRD Rules)",
      "category": "custom",
      "content": "**Short Rest** (1 hour):\n- Must have at least 1 Hit Point to start\n- No strenuous activity (reading, talking, eating, standing watch OK)\n- Spend Hit Point Dice to regain HP\n- Recharge features that refresh on Short Rest\n- **Interrupted by**: Rolling Initiative, casting spell (except cantrip), taking damage\n\n**Long Rest** (8 hours):\n- At least 6 hours sleep + 2 hours light activity\n- Must have at least 1 Hit Point to start\n- Benefits: Regain all HP, all spent Hit Dice, reduce Exhaustion by 1, restore ability scores\n- **Interrupted by**: Rolling Initiative, casting spell (except cantrip), taking damage, 1 hour walking/exertion\n- If rested 1+ hours before interruption, gain Short Rest benefits\n- Can resume after interruption (+1 hour per interruption)\n- Must wait 16 hours before starting another Long Rest\n\n**Campsite Facilities**:\n- **Campfire**: Provides warmth, light, cooking (prevents Extreme Cold hazard)\n- **Tents**: Shelter from precipitation (prevents Heavy Precipitation penalties)\n- **Watch Post**: Standing watch is light activity (allowed during rest)\n- **Capacity**: ~4-6 adventurers",
      "position": {"viewLevel": "adventure", "x": 90, "y": 90},
      "gmOnly": true,
